#
################################################################################
# OPEN FLAGS (for human review)
################################################################################
# F1 - "Computers Electronics & Industrial Controls" defaulted to single Kind
#      under R2; may split into 3 Collections later
# F2 - "Agriculture/Construction/Off-Road" defaulted to single Kind under R2
# F3 - "Automation Equipment & Services" mixes equipment and services in one
#      industry label
# F4 - "Venture Capital, Banking, Finance, Consulting" defaulted to single Kind
#      under R2
